@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_sruvxt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.cos(wp.exp(v0 + 0.74)))
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.36) * wp.sin(tmp + 0.40)) - tmp)
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v2 + 0.43)) - ((v1 + 0.14 / v1 + 0.01) - (v1 + 0.08 / tmp + 0.92)))
    tmp = 0.80
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v2 + 0.87)) * ((v1 + 0.74 - v2 + 0.56) + v2))
    data[tid] = v0
